text: Angelinae is a subfamily of mantids in the family Mantidae. At least three genera and about five described species are placed in the Angelinae. ==Genera== These three genera belong to the subfamily Angelinae: * Afrothespis Roy, 2006 * Catigaonopsis Vyjayandi, 2009 * Tagalomantis Hebard, 1920 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * Category:Mantidae Category:Mantodea subfamilies
title: Angelinae
